Title: Arlong the Saw
Description: Arlong the Saw is a sawshark fish-man.

Title: Cat Burglar
Description: Cat Burglar Nami is the navigator of the Straw Hat Pirates.

Title: Black Leg Sanji
Description: Sanji born as Vinsmoke Sanji, is the cook of the Straw Hat Pirates.

Title: Pirate Hunter Zoro
Description: Roronoa Zoro,[1] also known as Pirate Hunter Zoro,[8] is the combatant of the Straw Hat Pirates, and one of their two swordsmen.

Title: Soul King
Description: Soul King Brook is the musician of the Straw Hat Pirates,[15] and one of their two swordsmen.

Title: Knight of the Sea
Description: Knight of the Sea Jinbe[1] is the helmsman of the Straw Hat Pirates. He is the tenth member of the crew and the ninth to join, doing so during the Wano Country Arc.[18]

Title: Tony Tony Chopper
Description: ony Tony Chopper, also known as Cotton Candy Lover Chopper,[3] is the doctor of the Straw Hat Pirates.

Title: Kozuki Momonosuke
Description: Kozuki Momonosuke is an inhabitant of Wano Country and the son of the late daimyo of the Kuri region and patriarch of the Kozuki Family, Kozuki Oden.
